{"tid":1922243,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"★股市愈跌、買樓速度愈快，買樓收租作為避險工具","createTime":"2020-03-12T12:38:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-21T12:09:06.000Z","uid":19454,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"906e9da2989433957f6b408640ffb48518b8432e","tid":1922243,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T12:38:45.000Z","msg":"美聯鍾家豪表示，荃灣中心本月已錄超過15宗買賣成交，屋苑12座連天台單位，實用面積324方呎，開價480萬港元，同一時間獲數組準買家洽購，最後以478萬元售出，呎價14,753元，新買家為上車客，見單位罕有及銀行估凸價，故即時決定入市。<br />\n<br />\n鍾家豪指出，屋苑成交活躍，可買單位已買少見少，部分買家股市愈跌、買樓速度愈快，本月成交當中，有近30%為收租客，視買樓收租作為避險工具。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20200312/bkn-20200312142353339-0312_00842_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20200312%2Fbkn-20200312142353339-0312_00842_001.html&d=xKwzLSQbN%2FgnQ4qVdIYE%2BC1yjuEIKew%2F2lwpseS6mRM%3D&h=e262dfb2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20200312/bkn-20200312142353339-0312_00842_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"42502488304482b3fc220b59a5e1d41258897b2e","tid":1922243,"uid":19454,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T12:39:03.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=hAcZUD0aBDA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DhAcZUD0aBDA&d=xKwzLSQbN%2FgnQ4qVdIYE%2BC1yjuEIKew%2F2lwpseS6mRM%3D&h=4e739410\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=hAcZUD0aBDA</a>"},{"pid":"0dc5b23348c52ae93a4d0a4eacd560454d1f3d18","tid":1922243,"uid":19454,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T12:39:21.000Z","msg":"許留山因欠租遭入稟清盤<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1920364\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1920364</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大眾書局黃埔花園分店欠租 業主入稟追討逾52萬元<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1918943\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1918943</a>"},{"pid":"cadfcaf7750f1b66181f4